# {{ program_name }} — Information Database (IDB)

## Overview

The **Information Database (IDB)** contains all **operational technical publications** derived from the Knowledge Database through ASIGT generation.

## Structure

```
IDB/
├── csdb/               # Common Source Database
│   ├── dms/            # Data Modules
│   ├── pms/            # Publication Modules
│   ├── dmls/           # Data Module Lists
│   └── icn/            # Graphics (ICN)
│
├── applicability/      # Applicability data
│   ├── act/            # Applicability Cross-reference Table
│   ├── cct/            # Conditions Cross-reference Table
│   └── pct/            # Product Cross-reference Table
│
└── publications/       # Assembled publications
    ├── amm/            # Aircraft Maintenance Manual
    ├── ipc/            # Illustrated Parts Catalog
    ├── srm/            # Structural Repair Manual
    └── cmm/            # Component Maintenance Manuals
```

## Content Types

| Type | Format | Description |
|------|--------|-------------|
| Data Modules | S1000D XML | Individual information units |
| Publication Modules | S1000D XML | Publication structure |
| Graphics | CGM/PNG/SVG | Technical illustrations |
| Applicability | S1000D XML | Product configuration data |

